I am pretty sure this is a different error than any of the other stack overflow errors. I will try to put together a good failing example, but it looks from the stack trace that it is just recursing infinitely. Upping stack space doesn't help - I upped it all the way to 10 megs and it just hung. This was generated with 2.7.1 RC2.

Here is the top of the stack. This pattern just repeats all the way to the bottom of the stack. 
